he would inevitably become a bit irritable.

580
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:30,680
But you know,

581
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,400
aren't all men like that?

582
00:26:32,750 --> 00:26:34,700
But that damn snake demon Chilian,

583
00:26:35,030 --> 00:26:36,230
he took a liking to me.

584
00:26:36,750 --> 00:26:37,490
When I refused him,

585
00:26:37,490 --> 00:26:38,770
he killed my husband,

586
00:26:39,700 --> 00:26:40,890
and even forcibly abducted me

587
00:26:40,890 --> 00:26:43,420
to transform me into his current appearance,

588
00:26:44,350 --> 00:26:45,480
forcing me to stay by his side

589
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:46,480
as his substitute.

590
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:47,240
You can

591
