592
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:50,350
The last time you came to visit,

593
00:26:50,350 --> 00:26:51,790
the person you saw was me.

594
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,270
I was also

595
00:26:53,270 --> 00:26:54,880
forced to deceive you

596
00:26:55,510 --> 00:26:57,570
under his threats and intimidation.

597
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,680
You mean,

598
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:03,130
