599
00:27:04,510 --> 00:27:05,160
Yes.

600
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:08,840
Your husband treated you well, didn't he?

601
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:09,680
Yes.

602
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:11,880
My poor husband.

603
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:16,730
So where is Chilian now?

604
00:27:20,550 --> 00:27:21,440
Dead.

605
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:25,960
