606
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:28,000
I couldn't bear the humiliation anymore,

607
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:30,330
and wanted to avenge my husband even more.

608
00:27:30,670 --> 00:27:32,370
So I asked a snake catcher,

609
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,700
used the method he gave me

610
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:35,460
and fed Chi Lian realgar wine.

611
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,670
